Name: Slack - Send Message to Channel
Description: Send a message to a Slack channel
Params: channel: The name of the channel to send the message to
Params: message: The message to send
Share Tools: list_channels from github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/slack/code
Share Tools: search_channels from github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/slack/code
Share Tools: send_message from github.com/gptscript-ai/tools/apis/slack/code
Type: input

#!/bin/bash

cat << EOF

Use the Slack tools to find the channel specified within these <input> tags: <input>${CHANNEL}</input>.
Then, send the following message to the channel:

${MESSAGE}

EOF
